f-01:1Sa:2:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Even before the fat was burned, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 3:3","book":"Lev","chapter":3,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 3:16","book":"Lev","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" the priest’s servant would come and say to the one who was sacrificing, “Give the priest some meat to roast, because he won’t accept boiled meat from you —only raw.” "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 3:3","book":"Lev","chapter":3,"verse":3},{"label":"Lv 3:16","book":"Lev","chapter":3,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If that person said to him, “The fat must be burned first; then you can take whatever you want for yourself,” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 7:25","book":"Lev","chapter":7,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" the servant would reply, “No, I insist that you hand it over right now. If you don’t, I’ll take it by force!” "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 7:25","book":"Lev","chapter":7,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So the servants’ sin was very severe in the presence of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", because the men treated the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s offering with contempt. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mal 2:7–9","book":"Mal","chapter":2,"verse":7,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mal 2:7–9","book":"Mal","chapter":2,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Samuel served in the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s presence "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 2:11","book":"1Sa","chapter":2,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 3:1","book":"1Sa","chapter":3,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" —this mere boy was dressed in the linen ephod. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 2:28","book":"1Sa","chapter":2,"verse":28,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 2:11","book":"1Sa","chapter":2,"verse":11},{"label":"1Sm 3:1","book":"1Sa","chapter":3,"verse":1},{"label":"1Sm 2:28","book":"1Sa","chapter":2,"verse":28}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Each year his mother made him a little robe "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 28:31","book":"Exo","chapter":28,"verse":31,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and took it to him when she went with her husband to offer the annual sacrifice. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 1:3","book":"1Sa","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 1:21","book":"1Sa","chapter":1,"verse":21,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 28:31","book":"Exo","chapter":28,"verse":31},{"label":"1Sm 1:3","book":"1Sa","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"1Sm 1:21","book":"1Sa","chapter":1,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Eli would bless Elkanah and his wife: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 2:34","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":34,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" “May the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" give you children by this woman in place of the one she "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"DSS; MT reads he"},{"kind":"text","text":" has given to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":".” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 1:11","book":"1Sa","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 1:22","book":"1Sa","chapter":1,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 1:28","book":"1Sa","chapter":1,"verse":28,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" Then they would go home."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 2:34","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":34},{"label":"1Sm 1:11","book":"1Sa","chapter":1,"verse":11},{"label":"1Sm 1:22","book":"1Sa","chapter":1,"verse":22},{"label":"1Sm 1:28","book":"1Sa","chapter":1,"verse":28}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"DSS; MT reads he"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" paid attention to Hannah’s need, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 21:1","book":"Gen","chapter":21,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and she conceived and gave birth to three sons and two daughters. Meanwhile, the boy Samuel grew up in the presence of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 2:26","book":"1Sa","chapter":2,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 3:19–21","book":"1Sa","chapter":3,"verse":19,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 2:40","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":40,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 21:1","book":"Gen","chapter":21,"verse":1},{"label":"1Sm 2:26","book":"1Sa","chapter":2,"verse":26},{"label":"1Sm 3:19–21","book":"1Sa","chapter":3,"verse":19},{"label":"Lk 2:40","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":40}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now Eli was very old. He heard about everything his sons were doing to all Israel "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 2:13","book":"1Sa","chapter":2,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and how they were sleeping with the women who served at the entrance to the tent of meeting. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 38:8","book":"Exo","chapter":38,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 2:13","book":"1Sa","chapter":2,"verse":13},{"label":"Ex 38:8","book":"Exo","chapter":38,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He said to them, “Why are you doing these things? I have heard about your evil actions from all these people. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"No, my sons, the news I hear the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s people spreading is not good. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If one person sins against another, God can intercede for him, but if a person sins against the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", who can intercede for him?” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 15:30","book":"Num","chapter":15,"verse":30,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:26–27","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" But they would not listen to their father, since the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" intended to kill them. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 5:2","book":"Exo","chapter":5,"verse":2,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 14:17–18","book":"Exo","chapter":14,"verse":17,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 11:18–20","book":"Jos","chapter":11,"verse":18,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 15:30","book":"Num","chapter":15,"verse":30},{"label":"Heb 10:26–27","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":26},{"label":"Ex 5:2","book":"Exo","chapter":5,"verse":2},{"label":"Ex 14:17–18","book":"Exo","chapter":14,"verse":17},{"label":"Jos 11:18–20","book":"Jos","chapter":11,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"By contrast, the boy Samuel grew in stature and in favor with the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" and with people. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 2:52","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":52,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 2:52","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":52}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"A man of God came to Eli and said to him, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 33:1","book":"Deu","chapter":33,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 13:6","book":"Jdg","chapter":13,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" “This is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says: ‘Didn’t I reveal myself to your forefather’s family "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit the house of your father"},{"kind":"text","text":" when they were in Egypt and belonged to Pharaoh’s palace? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 4:14–16","book":"Exo","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 12:1","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 12:43","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":43,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 33:1","book":"Deu","chapter":33,"verse":1},{"label":"Jdg 13:6","book":"Jdg","chapter":13,"verse":6},{"label":"Ex 4:14–16","book":"Exo","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"Ex 12:1","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":1},{"label":"Ex 12:43","book":"Exo","chapter":12,"verse":43}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit the house of your father"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Out of all the tribes of Israel, I chose your house "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit selected him"},{"kind":"text","text":" to be my priests, to offer sacrifices on my altar, to burn incense, and to wear an ephod in my presence. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 28:1–4","book":"Exo","chapter":28,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" I also gave your forefather’s family all the Israelite food offerings. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 28:1–4","book":"Exo","chapter":28,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Lit selected him"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Why, then, do all of you despise my sacrifices and offerings that I require at the place of worship? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 12:5","book":"Deu","chapter":12,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" You have honored your sons more than me, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:37","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":37,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" by making yourselves fat with the best part of all of the offerings of my people Israel.’"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 12:5","book":"Deu","chapter":12,"verse":5},{"label":"Mt 10:37","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":37}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Therefore, this is the declaration of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", the God of Israel: ‘I did say that your family and your forefather’s family would walk before me forever. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 29:9","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 40:12–15","book":"Exo","chapter":40,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 25:10","book":"Num","chapter":25,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" But now,’ this is the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s declaration, ‘no longer! For those who honor me I will honor, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 50:23","book":"Psa","chapter":50,"verse":23,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" but those who despise me will be disgraced. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 2:26","book":"1Ki","chapter":2,"verse":26,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 29:9","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":9},{"label":"Ex 40:12–15","book":"Exo","chapter":40,"verse":12},{"label":"Nm 25:10","book":"Num","chapter":25,"verse":10},{"label":"Ps 50:23","book":"Psa","chapter":50,"verse":23},{"label":"1Kg 2:26","book":"1Ki","chapter":2,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Look, the days are coming when I will cut off your strength and the strength of your forefather’s family, so that none in your family will reach old age. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 4:11","book":"1Sa","chapter":4,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 22:17–20","book":"1Sa","chapter":22,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 4:11","book":"1Sa","chapter":4,"verse":11},{"label":"1Sm 22:17–20","book":"1Sa","chapter":22,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You will see distress in the place of worship, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 2:26","book":"1Ki","chapter":2,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in spite of all that is good in Israel, and no one in your family will ever again reach old age. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 8:4","book":"Zec","chapter":8,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Kg 2:26","book":"1Ki","chapter":2,"verse":26},{"label":"Zch 8:4","book":"Zec","chapter":8,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Any man from your family I do not cut off from my altar will bring grief "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit grief to your eyes"},{"kind":"text","text":" and sadness to you. All your descendants will die violently. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"DSS, LXX read die by the sword of men"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit die men"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit grief to your eyes"},{"marker":2,"text":"DSS, LXX read die by the sword of men"},{"marker":3,"text":"Lit die men"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This will be the sign that will come to you concerning your two sons Hophni and Phinehas: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 10:7","book":"1Sa","chapter":10,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 13:3","book":"1Ki","chapter":13,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" both of them will die on the same day. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 4:11","book":"1Sa","chapter":4,"verse":11,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 10:7","book":"1Sa","chapter":10,"verse":7},{"label":"1Kg 13:3","book":"1Ki","chapter":13,"verse":3},{"label":"1Sm 4:11","book":"1Sa","chapter":4,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:35","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“ ‘Then I will raise up a faithful priest "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 3:20","book":"1Sa","chapter":3,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" for myself. He will do whatever is in my heart and mind. I will establish a lasting dynasty for him, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 8:3","book":"1Sa","chapter":8,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 11:38","book":"1Ki","chapter":11,"verse":38,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and he will walk before my anointed one for all time. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 10:9","book":"1Sa","chapter":10,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 12:3","book":"1Sa","chapter":12,"verse":3,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 16:13","book":"1Sa","chapter":16,"verse":13,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 3:20","book":"1Sa","chapter":3,"verse":20},{"label":"1Sm 8:3","book":"1Sa","chapter":8,"verse":3},{"label":"1Kg 11:38","book":"1Ki","chapter":11,"verse":38},{"label":"1Sm 10:9","book":"1Sa","chapter":10,"verse":9},{"label":"1Sm 12:3","book":"1Sa","chapter":12,"verse":3},{"label":"1Sm 16:13","book":"1Sa","chapter":16,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Sa:2:36","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Anyone who is left in your family will come and bow down to him for a piece of silver or a loaf of bread. He will say: Please appoint me to some priestly office so I can have a piece of bread to eat.’”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099285425}